Setup the maxmind cron job

$ crontab -e

#Sometimes maxmind updates on the 2nd others on the 6th
0 0 10  * * /var/www/geoip/cron_get_geoip.sh

Zend Framework Libs Needed

Net/DNS
Net/DNSBL
Net/GeoIP